OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,FA "ruthless" gang has been jailed for
OL,7,Fmaking and selling "assassination
OL,8,Fkits" stocked with handguns,
OL,9,Fsilencers, ammunition and latex gloves.
OL,11,FThe kits were sold to the criminal
OL,12,Funderworld and were made in a
OL,13,Fbackgarden in Derbyshire - said by
OL,14,Fpolice to be "one of the biggest
OL,15,Ffirearm factories in the East
OL,16,FMidlands".
