OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,FOther weapons found in 64-year-old
OL,7,FRobert Knowles' home in Milton Avenue
OL,8,Fin Alfreton included crossbows,
OL,9,Fknives, axes, machetes, swords, gas-
OL,10,Fpowered weapons, and airguns.
OL,12,FThey were then sold on to criminals by
OL,13,FGary Hardy and Steven Houston, who
OL,14,Fwere found guilty at a trial.
OL,16,FHardy, 62, from Ravenshead in
OL,17,FNottinghamshire, was sentenced to 23
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,20,FHouston, 65, from Corley near
OL,21,FCoventry, was given 25 years in prison.
