OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,FKnowles, who admitted his crimes,
OL,7,Freceived a 13.5-year sentence.
OL,9,FTheir enterprise was uncovered when
OL,10,Fpolice stopped a vehicle in Measham,
OL,11,FLeicestershire, in August 2023 and
OL,12,Ffound a white box containing four guns
OL,13,Fwith Knowles' DNA on some of them.
OL,15,FWhen police arrived at Knowles' home,
OL,16,Fthey found him setting fire to
OL,17,Fevidence in his garden.
