OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,FProsecutors said the weapon kits were
OL,7,Fdistributed on a "significant scale",
OL,8,Fand added: "There was an expectation
OL,9,Fof substantial financial gain."
OL,11,FThe gang supplied the weapons to
OL,12,Fcriminals, including 23-year-old drug
OL,13,Fdealer Jason Hill, who was convicted
OL,14,Fof murder last year.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark Adas,
OL,17,Fof Nottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,18,F"These are ruthless individuals that
OL,19,Fhave a complete disregard for human
OL,20,Flife."
