OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,FHe said: "Each handgun had been
OL,7,Fthreaded to fit a silencer, which
OL,8,Fallowed the gun to be used discreetly
OL,9,Fat close quarters, meaning any
OL,10,Fpotential targets would be lucky to
OL,11,Fescape with their lives.
OL,13,F"The rounds of ammunition were
OL,14,Fconverted in such a way that upon
OL,15,Fimpact they expanded causing maximum
OL,16,Fdamage to any target.
