OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,F"Our team of detectives have now
OL,7,Fclosed arguably one of the biggest
OL,8,Ffirearm factories in the East Midlands
OL,9,Fand taken a large quantity of firearms
OL,10,Foff the streets."
OL,12,FHe continued: "If this operation had
OL,13,Fcontinued undetected, the strong
OL,14,Flikelihood is these weapons would have
OL,15,Fbeen used and people would have been
OL,16,Fkilled or seriously harmed.
