OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,F"To put this into context `
OL,7,Fconsidering that each assassination
OL,8,Fkit included 10 rounds of converted
OL,9,Fammunition, the seizure of more than
OL,10,F800 blank firing rounds and nearly 800
OL,11,Flead pellets indicates that the group
OL,12,Fhad the potential to supply up to 80
OL,13,Ffurther firearms packages.
OL,15,F"So far, we have identified eight
OL,16,Flocations across the country where
OL,17,Fthese specific converted firearms or
OL,18,Fammunition have been seized.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
