OL,3,CGang made 'assassination kits' in 'one
OL,4,Cof region's biggest gun factories'
OL,6,F"The majority were in the West
OL,7,FMidlands. This was therefore a well-
OL,8,Festablished and far-reaching criminal
OL,9,Fenterprise."
OL,11,FDefence lawyers pointed out Hardy's
OL,12,Fchronic health issues and said a
OL,13,Fprison sentence would impact his wife.
OL,15,FKnowles was said to be a "caring,
OL,16,Fhelpful, kind person that many in
OL,17,Fdifficulties can turn to", according
OL,18,Fto another defence barrister.
